  "slug": "opulence",
  "title": "Opulence",
  "description": "👑 Adds new decorative variants of expensive blocks like gold, diamond, and emerald!",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037215151134355476/Opulence_banner.png\" width=\"1473\" height=\"499\" /><img src=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pollen\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><center><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pollen\"><img src=\"https://tinyurl.com/pollen-opulence\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"28\" /></a>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/For%20MC_696014_all(1c9829-f9a500-ffffff-f9a500).svg?badge_style=for_the_badge\" width=\"103\" height=\"28\" />&nbsp;</center></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037231448312258581/Opulence_divider.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><center><h2>👑&nbsp;<strong>Decorative variants of valuable blocks!&nbsp;👑</strong></span></center></h2></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Opulence adds many new variants of ore blocks, currently including gold, diamond, and emerald. The goal of this mod is to give wealthy end game players more decorative options to use their resources for, and even open some new possibilities for building. Now you can finally build the luxurious diamond house of your dreams!</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><h3><strong>Features:</strong></span></h3></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Stairs and slabs for vanilla gold, diamond, and emerald blocks</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Cut variants of gold, diamond, and emerald blocks, along with their own stairs and slabs</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Engraved (chiseled) variants of gold, diamond, and emerald blocks</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Gold, diamond, and emerald pillars</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Iron, copper, and netherite blocks are planned, along with lamp blocks made from each ore.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037231448312258581/Opulence_divider.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"32\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><center><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037241923821371432/Gold_blocks.png\" alt=\"A collection of gold blocks\" width=\"600\" height=\"309\" /></center></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><center><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037241923020275762/Diamond_blocks.png\" alt=\"A collection of diamond blocks\" width=\"600\" height=\"310\" /></center></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><center><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037241923422924820/Emerald_Blocks.png\" alt=\"A collection of emerald blocks\" width=\"600\" height=\"310\" /></center></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1037215048180965417/1037231448312258581/Opulence_divider.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"32\" /></p>",
